{"tid":228822,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"工程技能交換","createTime":"2017-05-04T07:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T16:10:00.000Z","uid":71160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"115fe4015f06243ee520e02ed9c0285e1f1e685e","tid":228822,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位巴打好<br />\n我開呢個post係想交換技能。<br />\n我自己本身係建造業議會學水喉（1年制），拎左水喉同消防中工。我覺得好多時候都係hea多過做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我打算用技能換技能，我想學電器、機械，如果你識既話又對水喉有興趣的過，tg我：nevergiveup17<br />\n另外，我都會總結返係cic學過既知識比返你聽。<br />\n<br />\n我簡單講下水喉中工點考： 要識睇圖同埋畫圖，鑽孔，打喉碼，量碼喉長度，安裝喉到配件上面，屈之字喉，砌水箱。<br />\n合格條件係：唔漏水，尺寸準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A: <br />\nQ1: 點解要搵你學而唔去建造議會學?跟cic學每個月仲有錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nA: 因為跟cic學，讀佢個（水喉）成人班最快都要4個月先畢業，技能交換可以節省好多時間。 同埋你係cic報左一個course之後，要等一年後先再以報一個新course。講真，要由學到識做我覺我得根本唔洗四個月時間（起碼水喉係咁先），明白左點做之後練四五次出去考試一定無死，無錯係一定合格！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #yup一來# <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過跟cic學有師傅教你，二來會包曬你所有牌照（綠卡、安全卡、考試費）。不過缺點上面講左。<br />\n<br />\nQ2: 場地<br />\nA2: 新界火炭工廈（待定）<br />\n<br />\nQ3: 交換條件<br />\nA3: 起碼教授者對果項技能要有充份既認識，能清晰表達，有信心同耐性教好對方，並有能力解決到該技術既任何困難。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"02e52cbbf5894e45ea1212853530b2a64bdb3cfe","tid":228822,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:33:53.000Z","msg":"係學術台開左個post, 但無咩反應，係上班台開多過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869d996e2e173e699cbd7a9ed0ba8cc77eabe991","tid":228822,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:35:12.000Z","msg":"跟cic仲有個唔好，就你開始左個course, 讀讀下唔想讀既話，但又拎左佢d津貼的話呢，你要比返曬你拎過既所有津貼。同埋你考果d牌，佢要等你讀完成個course先比你"},{"pid":"8c17b2586065c611157b58b62b00daf2ac83cf14","tid":228822,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:41:54.000Z","msg":"係咪too long to read, 好似無咩反應咁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedc4ea877cee0f95224b1dd7ccc327a788b5f7d","tid":228822,"uid":70292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:49:52.000Z","msg":"我都想入建造業乎一門技能，但係九龍灣同上水教....車程都一粒鐘...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4459203fda45b647d2f87cf95fc62c7c5ab369","tid":228822,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T09:26:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想入建造業乎一門技能，但係九龍灣同上水教....車程都一粒鐘...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面講左跟cic優點同缼點"},{"pid":"9ec886f834e25126a3e5b51cd8deeec02ad8c3a4","tid":228822,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:21:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a679e42df6c6e3a39eed14dc94c7c2ea124aae3f","tid":228822,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/202309_1253dc2e8f23ec188893cea93c8aee9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F202309_1253dc2e8f23ec188893cea93c8aee9e.jpg&h=c48464c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係地盤要有中工牌先可以做相對既工種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e648a6138ca1ea08c5884a3ea7